{"tid":1612263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為了香港，你們願意付出更多？","createTime":"2019-10-02T07:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T12:03:18.000Z","uid":241626,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dac927094acb54ca30029b683abdc187bebe0552","tid":1612263,"uid":241626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T07:56:49.000Z","msg":"經歷左10月1日，我作為前線，我有好多嘅抱怨，但呢啲都唔重要。<br />\n<br />\n我見到香港人仲未完全覺醒。<br />\n<br />\n呢場係一場革命，14年雨傘運動，umbrella movement ，不過係一場運動，movement ，但有人記得佢另一個名嗎？佢係黃傘革命，雨傘革命。<br />\n<br />\n革命唔係運動，革命係決意要改變腐敗，係有改革性。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">我唔想2019只係一場運動，2019係一場時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n10月1，一個中五學生中槍，情況危殆。有一位手足為左救佢亦比狗拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n佢地全部都係青少年，係擁有抱負嘅青少年，為左香港嘅未來，佢地賭上自己嘅前途。<br />\n佢地無私，就係為左推倒強權，為弱勢嘅人發聲。<br />\n<br />\n我想問香港人，你地有一個決心去推革命？<br />\n革命係會流血，唔係一場嘉年華，每一個踏出屋企門口嘅你，有無咁嘅心理準備？<br />\n無嘅，我唔該你留翻係屋企，呢個係戰場，唔係講玩。<br />\n<br />\n帶得gear，就預左會犧牲，如果唔係帶黎做咩？企係後面呐喊算啦<br />\n<br />\n 每一個被捕嘅都係手足，佢地都有同一個理念，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我想問，香港人，願唔願意為佢地去奮鬥？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好比佢地白白犧牲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n邊個前線唔怕死，我地都怕，但理念、抱負勝過黑暗、死亡，我地先會繼續上前。<br />\n10月1，我見到好多偽勇武，帶左gear，仲企得後過和理非，你地又有幾大嘅抱負，幾大嘅理想？<br />\n<br />\n10月1已經過去，但未來依然存在<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你肯付出更多？<br />\n打一場精彩嘅仗得唔得</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"871a04e3732667293baf0c3dfb8643efa5b78b0a","tid":1612263,"uid":241626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:00:05.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"2e218e63b5cd8cb5974b47fea167617a1e337b8b","tid":1612263,"uid":200900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:00:53.000Z","msg":"前線要覺悟!<br />\n推"},{"pid":"72d019a8c3ec2f346f96c617b019ba85fec06c81","tid":1612263,"uid":234349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5986674605493de1c9be5299713d5081e624a98f","tid":1612263,"uid":241626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"推到熱門"},{"pid":"ec8f5fbc9899c3d39bf97f0ab594358b37c59dd8","tid":1612263,"uid":234349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f0ad527191fe14003702dd70bc635180b9b509e8","tid":1612263,"uid":199309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a4d92747e91c18c00271b4f793f7278de66b16","tid":1612263,"uid":234349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f8aae98e085ed3df96bf41ec726a5826ef7b92af","tid":1612263,"uid":234349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:03:37.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"800be5bcd7b85abd4484bd32a789b48909bde3f8","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:04:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b37e902e2e1ad1764edf96352474264d099c4865","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:04:37.000Z","msg":"推下你"},{"pid":"80121ae571494c9134b5a5a63cfddc02a25f3192","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:04:52.000Z","msg":"推下你老母"},{"pid":"079c5d6a40c2cfb88e4c3680b7ab640440d48bdd","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:05:04.000Z","msg":"推埋你老豆"},{"pid":"049a6e4aeaca2f9fd7bf44f500c847e9f33d197c","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:05:17.000Z","msg":"推曬你全家"},{"pid":"0778c4aed270e9e665b0178d21e0ce5945c511af","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313fa54f038e67ecd520470ad845b0b47832fc20","tid":1612263,"uid":199309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:07:02.000Z","msg":"驚係冇問題，但唔該知自己驚嘅就唔好扮型上前線，我地交條命俾你地，你地調頭走，對唔對得住被捕手足啊<br />\n前線唔係俾你圍威喂嘅地方啊，冇覺悟唔緊要，企後啲，知唔知你地累撚死幾多人啊"},{"pid":"07d92c48d308f12618959f967c10ec7697f2b59b","tid":1612263,"uid":199309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:07:16.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"4a5eaa42c67e3776c84e0ebf098d976fb5a15cbc","tid":1612263,"uid":234349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:10:22.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"4f920c0ff807a02ad3778f470c3334ce842df940","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"成堆偽勇武塞撚曬係度 又唔撚係要打"},{"pid":"743cd3c209be64006002d004584a7ae48a973672","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:15:23.000Z","msg":"一聽到有防暴就冚家走撚曬"},{"pid":"ec2dd3848893df4c7e4ebb115194e5d1e701fced","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:52:18.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"0ba9412c1d476a81adcc17b093894fb4618e77d4","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:52:29.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"db8dbfaa844daa90a0f81f83add61158c9395512","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"cc722d52f45e0bee741ca17736d66e4095b75fd4","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:52:52.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"db95b1f61bb875be1fc3c84806136c5ba52fc785","tid":1612263,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"推5"}]}